    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure? This car is in really solid shape and runs like a charm. It\u2019s been so good to me, but it\u2019s finally time for it to find a new home. You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road! It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come check it out\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical upgrade for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings, providing the tactile feedback and mechanical grip these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and immediate throttle response. This is a mechanically sorted M-car ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
