    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained Executive Sport Sedan in a timeless Metallic Charcoal finish. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and performance, ideal for a discerning driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, accented by original alloy wheels; while there are a few minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia, the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment where the premium black leather remains supple, showing only gentle softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and robust. It boasts a documented service log, including a recent preventative maintenance inspection and a fresh set of high-performance tires. Garage-kept and treated with care, this sedan offers a sophisticated driving experience with the reliability of a well-loved machine.",
      "price": 34800.0,
